{"word":"Cedar","slug":"cedar","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Cedar</b> Valuable for building purposes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=9&verse=10'>Isa 9:10</a><br/> David's ample provision of, in Jerusalem, for the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=1&verse=15'>2Ch 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=4'>2Ch 2:4</a><br/> Furnished by Hiram, king of Tyre, for Solomon's temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=10'>1Ki 5:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=11'>1Ki 9:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=16'>2Ch 2:16</a><br/> Used in rebuilding the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=7'>Ezr 3:7</a><br/> Used in David's palace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=11'>2Sa 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=17&verse=1'>1Ch 17:1</a><br/> Used in Solomon's palace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=2'>1Ki 7:2</a><br/> Used for masts of ships<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=5'>Eze 27:5</a><br/> Used in purifications<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=4'>Lev 14:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=6'>Lev 14:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=52'>Lev 14:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=6'>Num 19:6</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=72&verse=16'>Psa 72:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=92&verse=12'>Psa 92:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=13'>Isa 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=14&verse=8'>Isa 14:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=7'>Jer 22:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=31&verse=3'>Eze 31:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=11&verse=2'>Zec 11:2</a>"}]}